    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/IndiaEats/CSS/ab.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        
        <h1>India Eats</h1>
        <p><p>Your solution for food waste management</p><p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="http://localhost/IndiaEats/index.php/">Home</a>
        <a href="http://localhost/IndiaEats/about.php/">About Us</a>
        <a href="http://localhost/IndiaEats/cont.php/">Contact Us</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="slideshow-container">
                <img class="slides active-slide" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Slide 1">
                <img class="slides" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Slide 2">
                <img class="slides" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Slide 3">
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>At India Eats, we believe that food is a fundamental human right and that no one should go hungry while perfectly good food goes to waste. Our mission is to reduce food waste and ensure that surplus food reaches those who need it the most.</p>
                <p>With our innovative platform, users can easily donate surplus food instead of discarding it. Whether you're a restaurant, a grocery store, or an individual with excess food, you can make a difference by sharing what you have.</p>
                <p>Our application allows users to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Login and create a profile.</li>
                    <li>View available food in their area that can be donated.</li>
                    <li>Connect with food banks, shelters, and other organizations in need of food donations.</li>
                    <li>Track their donations and see the impact they are making in their community.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Food is too valuable to waste. Join us in our effort to fight hunger and reduce food waste. Together, we can create a more sustainable and equitable food system.</p>
                <p>Login to our webpage and start making a difference today!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 All rights reserved by India Eats</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        let slideIndex = 0;
        const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slides');

        function showSlides() {
            slides.forEach((slide, index) => {
                slide.style.display = 'none';
                if (index === slideIndex) {
                    slide.style.display = 'block';
                }
            });

            slideIndex = (slideIndex + 1) % slides.length;
        }

        setInterval(showSlides, 3000); // Change image every 3 seconds
    </script>
</body>
